{"tid":2080201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國參議院一致通過《香港自治法案》    可制裁損害港自治人士及企業","createTime":"2020-06-26T09:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T09:26:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3bf7482d530b14fc55ce1cd3e9293b5831fca983","tid":2080201,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T09:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VvfXayjKOxWwV8IZg7bvlw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200626a061147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVvfXayjKOxWwV8IZg7bvlw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200626a061147.jpg&h=84ac2515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】美國參議院一致通過《香港自治法案》，可制裁美方認為損害香港自治的人士及<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">企業</span></span></strong>。預料法案可獲民主黨控制的眾議院通過，之後交由總統特朗普簽署生效。<br />\n<br />\n法案容許制裁個別人士或企業，以及與他們有生意往來的銀行。法案原本上星期通過，但應特朗普政府要求作出技術修訂而推遲。<br />\n<br />\n推動法案的民主黨參議員范霍頓表示，法案向北京發出清楚訊息，損害香港自治會招致後果。共和黨參議員霍利認為，這次可能是阻止北京摧毀香港僅存自由的最後機會。<br />\n<br />\n法案原本在今個月較早前通過，但有共和黨議員應政府要求進行技術修訂而押後。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/國安法-美國參議院-致通過-香港自治法案-可制裁損害港自治人士及企業-220900952.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E9%99%A2-%E8%87%B4%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E6%90%8D%E5%AE%B3%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%8A%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD-220900952.html&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2hwbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=bace0f4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/國安法-美國參議院-致通過-香港自治法案-可制裁損害港自治人士及企業-220900952.html</a>"},{"pid":"a2682235991bab4ef1b6bde20ed3c7aa1ae37aec","tid":2080201,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T09:11:32.000Z","msg":"有邊D企業係候選名單？"},{"pid":"217f382709c91d003bb6abc29c6384c9b4719017","tid":2080201,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T09:21:04.000Z","msg":"一致通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前仲話有十幾個参議員反對既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb4e4f6b77c7a97f703d7781657e8edbf317268","tid":2080201,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T09:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76ac8f7794448d1695f28395e11d3283b623dec","tid":2080201,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"217f382709c91d003bb6abc29c6384c9b4719017","tid":2080201,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T09:21:04.000Z","msg":"一致通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前仲話有十幾個参議員反對既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T09:26:21.000Z","msg":"反對唔夠辣<br />\n<br />\n依家呢個係加辣版"}]}